/*
History of c++:
->It was de eloped by Bjarne Stroustrup at AT&T Bell Laboratories in Murray Hill, New Jersey, USA, in the early 1980's.

Facts: 
->C++'s OOP aspect was inspired by a computer simulation language called Simula67
->ava is written in C++
->Major operating systems of modern times are written in c++
->C++ is worlds 4th most used programming language

Features of c++
->C++ is a middle level language(which means it can support both low level and high level programming)
->C++ supports principles of object oriented pradigm
->C++ joins three separate programming traditions 
   *->the procedural language tradtion, represented by c;
   *->the object-oriented language tradtion, represented by the class enhancements c++ adds to c;
   *->generic programming, supported by c++ templates*/


